Package: gleam
Title: GLEAM Herd Simulation and Livestock Dynamics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements steady-state herd simulation components used in the Global Livestock 
    Environmental Assessment Model (GLEAM), including population structure, offtake 
    flows, demographic transitions, and cohort-level weight metrics. Designed to be 
    modular, testable, and integrated with downstream feed and emissions models.
